com.snapon.sbs.dns.emailsettings

Class EmailTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snapon.sbs.dns.emailsettings.EmailTemplate

  • public class EmailTemplate
extends Object
    This class represents en email template. Each template can only be specifically used depending on the security class of the user.
